<h1>Hike a Trail!</h1>
<p>Brukner Nature Center has 6 miles of nature trails that allow you to search for wildlife on quiet mulch trails through wooldland, wetland, and prairie.

</p>
<ul>
    <li>Trails are open from sunrise to sunset only!
</li>
    <li>No pets allowed - they scare our wildlife!
</li>
    <li>No smoking or vaping on BNC property!
</li>
<li>Please stay on the trails, especially through the muddy parts!  Off-trail exploration causes erosion, damages wildflowers, & depletes habitat by widening trails.
</li>
<li>
    Please take all trash home with you!

</li>
</ul>

